    <title>Using Emacs - Intro to Org Mode</title>
    <id>http://cestlaz.github.io/posts/using-emacs-2-org/</id>
    <updated>2016-05-23T13:29:36-04:00</updated>
    <published>2016-05-23T13:29:36-04:00</published>
